==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A place of [[worship]], smaller than, or [[subordinate]] to a  [[church]].
# A place of worship in a [[civil]] [[institution]] such as an [[airport]], [[prison]] etc.
# A [[funeral]] [[home]], or a [[room]] in one for holding funeral [[service]]s.

